OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784132319
OL,3,CWill it rain for the start of the
OL,4,Cschool holidays?
OL,6,FWe're barely half way through the
OL,7,Fsummer, and we've already seen record
OL,8,Fbreaking temperatures - so what's to
OL,9,Fcome as we roll towards the school
OL,10,Fholidays?
OL,12,FThis is one of our longest runs of
OL,13,Fhigh temperatures since 2006, we've
OL,14,Fnow had more than 10 days of
OL,15,Ftemperatures above 30C.
OL,17,FIt would be typical of the British
OL,18,Fweather to turn as soon as the school
OL,19,Fterm ends, but here's the current
OL,20,Fforecast for the next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
